        <Summary>An audio-player, written with Qt4 library</Summary>
        <Description>Qmmp is an audio-player, written with Qt4 library. It's similar to Winamp or Xmms. Also supports Xmms and Winamp skins. qmmp-skins package in Contrib repository is recommended, too.</Description>
        <Archive sha1sum="8296f5899088b61d8d965e5f38511d357b7b8383" type="tarbz2">http://qmmp.ylsoftware.com/files/qmmp-0.2.4.tar.bz2</Archive>
